This program performs following features:

i.   Create student report card record.
ii.  Display all students’ report card record. Can sort the data by name and marks. (Insertion Sort)
iii. Display specific student’s report card record. (Binary Searching)
iv.  Display all students’ grade report.
v.   Modify student’s report card record. (Binary Searching)
vi.  Delete student record. (Delete)


Instructions:
1. Copy the latest version of Code.
2. Open Codeblocks / VSCode IDE.
3. Open Workspace / Project Folder in IDE.
4. Paste The code as CPP file.
6. Run the program & Debug it.
